df.r <- reshape(df, idvar = "Var2", timevar = "Var1", direction = "wide")
dat1 <- df.r
dat1[] <- lapply(dat1[], function(x){
  # Check if the column is numeric
  if (is.numeric(x)){
    return(x/sum(x)*100)
  } else{
    return(x)
  }
})
